# Optional .env for rx-ui. The binary works without ANY of these
# (zero-config first-run: auto-generates JWT_SECRET into data/jwt_secret,
# creates panel.db, downloads xray, bootstraps admin/admin).
#
# Override here only if you want:
#   - Pre-set secret from a vault / secrets manager
#   - Bind to a public interface (PANEL_HOST=0.0.0.0)
#   - Use a system xray instead of the bundled one
#   - More verbose logs
#
# Anything left commented out falls back to the defaults documented in
# README.md § Environment.

# JWT_SECRET=replace-with-32+chars-from-secrets-manager
# DATABASE_URL=sqlite://data/panel.db
# PANEL_HOST=0.0.0.0
# PANEL_PORT=8080
# XRAY_BINARY=/usr/local/bin/xray
# XRAY_CONFIG=/etc/rx-ui/xray-config.json
# RUST_LOG=rx_ui=debug,tower_http=info,sqlx=warn
